graph TD
    classDef legacy fill:#3a1f1f,stroke:#ff4d4d,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef vox fill:#143040,stroke:#00e5ff,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef core fill:#2b0d3d,stroke:#a64dff,stroke-width:3px;

    subgraph Legacy [Legacy Fragmentation]
        direction TB
        TS[TypeScript Client]:::legacy --> API[REST / GraphQL]:::legacy
        API --> Controllers[Server Controllers]:::legacy
        Controllers --> ORM[ORM / Data Access]:::legacy
        ORM --> DB[(Postgres Database)]:::legacy
    end

    subgraph Unified [Vox Unification]
        direction TB
        SRC[.vox Source File]:::vox --> COMPILER((VOX COMPILER)):::core
        
        COMPILER --> |Frontend Projection| WEBIR(WebIR):::vox
        COMPILER --> |Backend Lowering| HIR(HIR):::vox
        
        WEBIR --> TSX[React Islands & TSX]:::vox
        HIR --> ROUTE[Route Contracts]:::vox
        HIR --> SQL[(SQLite Schema)]:::vox
    end
